profile:
Ben Kuypers Design Group is your one stop kitchen/bath design and renovation service here in Kelowna. 

Supplying design, consulting and renovation services with an association of established suppliers in the Okanogan. 

You receive an attention to detail and a level of service which is demonstrated by client reviews. Our focus is on your referral.

Thirty years providing innovative design and renovating new and existing homes in Calgary.
 
Formally trained as a draftsman and artist in Toronto, combining the technical and the creative to achieve the most functional and beautiful remodelling projects.
 
Served as an executive member of the National Kitchen & Bath Assoc. (NKBA) when it was first introduced to Western Canada in the early 1990's.
 
Kitchen and bath design is our speciality while also providing space planning and interior design services.

View the gallery of projects and check the many reviews by previous customers.
